    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Federal Solar Tax Credit (ITC):</strong> Claim 30% of your total system cost as a tax credit.</li>
      <li><strong>California Self-Generation Incentive Program (SGIP):</strong> Get rebates for solar battery storage systems.</li>
      <li><strong>Local Utility Rebates:</strong> Additional cash-back offers from utilities like PG&E, SCE, SDG&E.</li>
      <li><strong>Net Energy Metering (NEM 3.0):</strong> Sell excess energy back to the grid at reduced but still valuable rates.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

